dct_title_s: Insurance maps of the New Jersey coast : volume one
dct_description_sm: Includes title, key map and index sheets. Index for maps of Long Branch, South Elberon, West Long Branch & Norwood Park; Monmouth Beach; Sea Bright; Normandie by the Sea, Highland Beach, Oakhurst, Oceanport & Little Silver; Fair Haven; Oceanic and East Oceanic; Rumson Road; Highlands; Water Witch Park; Navesink; Atlantic Highlands.
